#

Tofu and Sweet Potato Hash

30 min
$10
300 kcal
Difficulty: 15%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

EasyHealthyComfort Food

Description

A hearty and flavorful dish combining crispy tofu and sweet potatoes, perfect for breakfast or brunch!

Ingredients

  • tofu: 1 block (14 oz)
  • sweet potato: 2 medium
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • bell pepper (any color): 1
  • onion: 1 small
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • spinach (optional): 2 cups
